        "#### 4 Proccesses\n",
        "\n",
        "```bash\n",
        "$ time mpirun -np 4 ./mpi_train\n",
        "Went parallel: rank 2 of 4 doing work for 450 steps\n",
        "Went parallel: rank 3 of 4 doing work for 450 steps\n",
        "Will divide up work for input table of size = 1801\n",
        "Went parallel: rank 0 of 4 doing work for 450 steps\n",
        "Went parallel: rank 1 of 4 doing work for 450 steps\n",
        "Sum of DefaultProfile for rank 0 of 4 on LAPTOP-O8LRLROT is 87.142860\n",
        "Sum of DefaultProfile for rank 1 of 4 on LAPTOP-O8LRLROT is 0.000000\n",
